<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
  <message name="injectListJSON" id="injectListJSON"/>
  <process isExecutable="true" name="2-step Twitter Test Process" id="twittertest">
    <startEvent name="Start" id="startevent1"/>
    <endEvent name="End" id="endevent1"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_test1_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Form Task 1" id="form1"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Fact Task 1" id="fact1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_test1_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="form2" sourceRef="startevent1" id="flow1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="form1" id="flow3"/>
    <boundaryEvent cancelActivity="false" attachedToRef="form1" name="Message" id="boundarymessage1">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
    </boundaryEvent>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Fact Task 2" id="fact2">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_test2_fact</activiti:string>

    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact3" sourceRef="fact2" id="flow4"/>

        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">

    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact4" sourceRef="fact3" id="flow5"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Fact Task 4" id="fact4">

    </serviceTask>

    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_test2_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Form Task 2" id="form2"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Read_Obj_toFields" name="save keys and tokens" id="servicetask1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>

        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">

        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">

        </activiti:field>

      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask2" sourceRef="form2" id="flow11"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact2" sourceRef="servicetask2" id="flow12"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact2" sourceRef="fact1" id="flow13"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_List_Objs" name="save keys and tokens" id="servicetask3">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask3" sourceRef="form2" id="flow14"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact3" sourceRef="servicetask3" id="flow15"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Create_Obj_fromFields" name="save keys and tokens" id="servicetask4">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">

        </activiti:field>

        </activiti:field>

      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Update_Obj_fromFields" name="save keys and tokens" id="servicetask5">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask4" sourceRef="form2" id="flow16"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask5" sourceRef="form2" id="flow17"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact4" sourceRef="servicetask4" id="flow18"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact5" sourceRef="servicetask5" id="flow19"/>
  </process>

flow.name: io.point.Twitter_provider
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">
  <process id="io.point.Twitter_provider" name="io.point.Twitter_provider" isExecutable="true">
    <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start"/>
    <serviceTask id="GETobjs" name="List Objects" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_List_Objs">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask id="GETobjtypes" name="List Records" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_List_Recs">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask id="GETobj" name="Read Record" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Read_Obj_toFields">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask id="PUTobj" name="Update Record" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Update_Obj_fromFields">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask id="GETobj2" name="Read Record Again" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Read_Obj_toFields">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>{$accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask id="POSTobj" name="Create Record" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Create_Obj_fromFields">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="data">
          <activiti:expression>${data}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway1" name="Exclusive Gateway" default="default"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="exclusivegateway1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow10" sourceRef="PUTobj" targetRef="GETobj2"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow12" name="GETOBJS" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="GETobjs">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GETOBJS"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow13" name="GETRECS" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="GETobjtypes">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GETRECS"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow14" name="GET" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="GETobj">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GET"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow15" name="PUT" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="PUTobj">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "PUT" || apidata_method == "PATCH"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow20" name="POST" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="POSTobj">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method=="POST"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow16" sourceRef="GETobj2" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow17" sourceRef="GETobj" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow18" sourceRef="GETobjtypes" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow19" sourceRef="GETobjs" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow21" sourceRef="POSTobj" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="default" name="Unsupported" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <userTask id="usertask1" name="Default" activiti:formKey="poi_default_view"/>
    <userTask id="usertask2" name="Tweet" activiti:formKey="poi_tweet_view"/>
    <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End"/>
